<i>noun</i>: 돌부처 [돌ː부처] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>돌부처 [돌ː부처]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stone Buddha statue</dd><br>
<dd>돌로 만든 불상.</dd><br>
<dd>A statue of Buddha made of stone.</dd><br>
<dd>2. bigot; stick in the mud</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 고지식하고 감정에 따라 마음이 움직이지 않는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A person who is uncompromising and intractable, and does not act the way he/she feels.</dd><br>
<dd>3. big-hearted person; philanthropist</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 지나치게 너그럽고 착한 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A person who is excessively generous and warm-hearted.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>